                    Nature's RNG Disclaimer:
                </div>
                <div class="text-[11px] sm:text-[13px] text-green-200/80 font-medium tracking-wide leading-relaxed">
                    All garden rune drops are rooted in probability. ETA values are <span class="text-green-300 font-bold">estimated chances, not guarantees</span>. Your harvest may bloom earlier or later depending on your luck!
